OL,5,Cover cuts
OL,7,FLecturers at four Scottish
OL,8,Funiversities are voting on possible
OL,9,Fstrike action in four separate
OL,10,Fdisputes over proposed budget cuts and
OL,11,Fjob losses.
OL,13,FUniversity and College Union (UCU)
OL,14,Fmembers at Aberdeen, Stirling, Heriot-
OL,15,FWatt and Strathclyde are being asked
OL,16,Fwhether they support strike action,
OL,17,Fand also whether they are willing to
OL,18,Ftake action short of a strike.
