OL,7,FThe latter can include things such as
OL,8,Fworking to contract, refusing to cover
OL,9,Ffor absent colleagues or do voluntary
OL,10,Factivities, and marking and assessment
OL,11,Fboycotts.
OL,13,FIf they vote in favour, the members
OL,14,Fwill then decide what action to take
OL,15,Fand how to pursue the dispute with
OL,16,Ftheir employer.
