OL,5,Cover cuts
OL,7,FThe union said the move comes after
OL,8,Fsenior management at all four
OL,9,Funiversities refused to rule out
OL,10,Fcompulsory redundancies as part of
OL,11,Ftheir attempts to cut costs.
OL,13,FThe UCU said 40 staff have already
OL,14,Fleft Aberdeen University voluntarily
OL,15,Funder its Adapting for Continued
OL,16,FSuccess programme, but the university
OL,17,Fhas refused to rule out compulsory
OL,18,Fredundancies.
