OL,4,Cpossible strike action in disputes
OL,5,Cover cuts
OL,7,FAt Heriot-Watt, senior management have
OL,8,Frefused to rule out compulsory exits
OL,9,Fas part of plans to cut at least 41
OL,10,Fjob losses in Scotland, and 10 at its
OL,11,Fcampus in Malaysia.
OL,13,FMeanwhile at Stirling, 175 staff have
OL,14,Falready left voluntarily in recent
OL,15,Fmonths, but further cuts ` including
OL,16,Fpossible compulsory redundancies ` are
OL,17,Fplanned, which the union said jarred
OL,18,Fwith principal Gerry McCormac recently
OL,19,Fbecoming the highest-paid principal in
OL,20,Fthe country.
