OL,7,FFinally, Strathclyde is planning to
OL,8,Fcut 76 jobs as it bids to make savings
OL,9,Fof #35 million, with the UCU calling
OL,10,Ffor it to engage in meaningful
OL,11,Fconsultation on its planned changes.
OL,13,FThe threat of industrial action comes
OL,14,Fafter recent walkouts over similar
OL,15,Fdisputes at the University of Dundee,
OL,16,Fthe University of Edinburgh, and the
OL,17,FUniversity of the Highlands and
OL,18,FIslands (UHI).
