OL,8,FChristmas, while UCU members at
OL,9,FEdinburgh voted to suspend strike
OL,10,Faction following a number of
OL,11,Fconcessions from the university,
OL,12,Fincluding a commitment of no
OL,13,Fcompulsory redundancies during the
OL,14,Fcurrent academic year.
