OL,7,FJo Grady, UCU general secretary, said:
OL,8,F"We're just days into the New Year and
OL,9,Fonce again universities across
OL,10,FScotland are facing the possibility of
OL,11,Findustrial action, with members being
OL,12,Fforced to vote for strike action to
OL,13,Fdefend jobs and force university
OL,14,Fprincipals to rule out compulsory
OL,15,Fredundancies.
