OL,7,F"With a record number of jobs being
OL,8,Fcut across Scottish universities, the
OL,9,Fprincipals at Stirling and Heriot-Watt
OL,10,Fand those at Strathclyde and Aberdeen,
OL,11,Fwho are starting off their time as
OL,12,Fprincipals in the most disappointing
OL,13,Fway, need to listen to their staff and
OL,14,Fcommit to ruling out compulsory
OL,15,Fredundancies before these disputes
OL,16,Fescalate into strikes with resulting
OL,17,Fdisruption to students."
