OL,7,FAll four strike ballots open on Monday
OL,8,Fand will remain open into February,
OL,9,Fwith Strathclyde's ballot closing on
OL,10,FFebruary 9, followed by Heriot-Watt
OL,11,Fand Aberdeen on February 16, and
OL,12,FStirling on February 17.
OL,14,FA University of Aberdeen spokesperson
OL,15,Fsaid: "There have been drop-in
OL,16,Fsessions and workshops about Adapting
OL,17,Ffor Continued Success and more are
OL,18,Ftaking place in January.
